{"tid":958533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗咬狗]小西灣寵物公園打傷遛狗男女 反黑拘5男女","createTime":"2018-12-28T01:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T07:07:48.000Z","uid":6242,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9cfa83e78ffdbbc1fb16c9be63884a89c5c29f10","tid":958533,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:31:37.000Z","msg":"柴灣小西灣富康街寵物公園發生的傷人及踢狗案，東區警區反三合會行動組人員接手調查案件，於昨日(12月27日)晚上約11時30分，在小西灣邨拘捕年齡介乎24至34歲的四名男子和一名女子，涉嫌在公眾地方打架，其中一名30歲男子亦涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害。探員凌晨將一名男子押返小西灣邨瑞發樓搜查。被捕男女現正被扣留調查。<br />\n事發前晚11時許，一名姓黃63歲女子到來遛狗，其間她的柴犬撲向另一隻狗，女狗主大怒雙方發生爭執，女狗主其後「吹雞」召來五名男子，他們推倒黃婦並腳踢她的狗隻。一名姓陳27歲遛狗男子，上前阻止期間亦被眾人毆打，眾男女其後逃去。兩男女分別腳傷背痛，以及額頭、眼角及鼻傷。<br />\n警員接報到場經初步調查，案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害、殘酷對待動物及普通襲擊，追緝該六名年齡約20至40歲男女。兩名事主清醒送東區醫院治理，黃婦的狗隻被送往愛護動物協會檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181228/59077903?fbclid=IwAR20JPre28QujMIVJ0rO5pr-wTUr4uLi9lhHFx5EHTXcKRq0Wl6d9VAZXuc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59077903%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR20JPre28QujMIVJ0rO5pr-wTUr4uLi9lhHFx5EHTXcKRq0Wl6d9VAZXuc&d=71pwVW65x16IUdXCvZTcCAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a6be5a16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59077903%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR20JPre28QujMIVJ0rO5pr-wTUr4uLi9lhHFx5EHTXcKRq0Wl6d9VAZXuc&h=bcdb4089\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181228/59077903?fbclid=IwAR20JPre28QujMIVJ0rO5pr-wTUr4uLi9lhHFx5EHTXcKRq0Wl6d9VAZXuc</a><br />\n<br />\n養狗養到吹雞, 住屋邨都養得咁高調<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323fe9d70b53a90e57719c6f45b2fc8b53fc0553","tid":958533,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:15:15.000Z","msg":"狗狗好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f